    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的右翼盟友抓住巴西选举前禁令的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/elon-musk-s-right-wing-allies-seize-on-brazil-x-ban-heading-into-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西对社交媒体平台 X 的禁令可能会给所有者埃隆·马斯克带来经济挫折，但对这位亿万富翁及其右翼盟友来说，这也是一个潜在的政治机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/elon-musk-s-right-wing-allies-seize-on-brazil-x-ban-heading-into-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰三名部长提议辞职 进行大规模改组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着乌克兰这个饱受战争摧残的国家面临俄罗斯不断增多的导弹袭击，外界猜测该国将进行更大范围的政府改组，三名内阁部长于周二提交了辞呈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:54:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥议员在体育中心开会以躲避抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[示威者在墨西哥下议院周围形成人链，迫使议员们转移到体育中心，抗议总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的司法改革法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:48:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基再次恳求俄罗斯导弹袭击造成 51 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/zelenskiy-says-41-people-killed-in-russian-strike-on-poltava</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基强调要部署防空系统，此前俄罗斯导弹袭击造成 50 多人死亡，这是自 2022 年 2 月克里姆林宫入侵以来最致命的袭击之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/zelenskiy-says-41-people-killed-in-russian-strike-on-poltava</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
